                <h2 id="dep-head" >Emergency Room</h2>
                <p>An emergency department (ED), also known as an accident and emergency department (A&E), emergency room (ER), emergency ward
                     (EW) or casualty department, is a medical treatment facility specializing in emergency medicine, 
                     the acute care of patients who present without prior appointment; either by their own means or by that of an ambulance.
                      The emergency department is usually found in a hospital or other primary care center.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
