                <h2 id="dep-head" >Enough Bed</h2>
                <p>A hospital bed or hospital cot is a bed specially designed for hospitalized patients or others
                     in need of some form of health care. These beds have special features both for the comfort 
                     and well-being of the patient and for the convenience of health care workers. Common features
                      include adjustable height for the entire bed, the head, and the feet, adjustable side rails,
                       and electronic buttons to operate both the bed and other nearby electronic devices.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
